<p>Welcome to WinWinLabs, where you can make donations to worthy causes, play games, and win prizes. We want to make sure you understand some important legal terms related to your participation in the games and the prizes you might win.</p>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Donations:</strong> By making a donation, you are providing financial support to our non-profit organization. These donations help us and other beneficiaries carry out our missions, so thank you! Generally, donations to non-profits are tax deductible.</li>
        <li><strong>Games:</strong> For your donation, we offer a variety of games you can play: Minecraft, 2048, Puzzle, and Challenge, with many more on our radar. You donâ€™t have to play, but why not? All of our games require some skill, but because some of our games have an element of chance, they are not allowed in some locations.</li>
