        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you register and participate in our games, we may collect certain personal information from you. Specifically in the challenge games it is sometimes necessary to capture your contact information. Please review our privacy policy to understand how we handle and protect your data.</li>
    </ol>
<p>By using our website, making donations, and participating in the games, you agree to abide by these terms and any other rules and guidelines provided on our website. If you have any questions or concerns about the legal aspects of our website or your participation, please don't hesitate to contact us. Thank you for supporting us, and we hope you have a great time playing games on our platform!</p>